6.004">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31221403/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=A+phantom+study+comparing+technical+image+quality+of+five+breast+tomosynthesis+systems&amp;author=VM+Sundell&amp;author=M+Jousi&amp;author=K+Hukkinen&amp;author=R+Blanco&amp;author=T+M%C3%A4kel%C3%A4&amp;author=T+Kaasalainen&amp;publication_year=2019&amp;journal=Phys+Med&amp;pages=122-130&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.ejmp.2019.06.004&amp;pmid=31221403">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">106.</div><div id="r106" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">EUREF - European Reference Organisation for Quality Assured Breast Screening and Diagnostic Services. Breast Tomosynthesis Quality Control Protocol (version 1.03); <a href="https://www.euref.org/european-guidelines/physico-technical-protocol">https://www.euref.org/european-guidelines/physico-technical-protocol</a>. Updated March 2018. Accessed April 28, 2020.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Breast+Tomosynthesis+Quality+Control+Protocol+%28version+1.03%29&amp;author=EUREF+-+European+Reference+Organisation+for+Quality+Assured+Breast+Screening+and+Diagnostic+Services">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">107.</div><div id="r107" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">U.S. FDA Mammography Quality Standards Act (MQSA) - Digital Breast Tomosynthesis (DBT) System requirements. <a href="https://www.fda.gov/radiation-emitting-products/facility-certification-and-inspection-mqsa/digital-breast-tomosynthesis-dbt-system">https://www.fda.gov/radiation-emitting-products/facility-certification-and-inspection-mqsa/digital-breast-tomosynthe